## User Settings

Add these to your **user** `settings.json` (the workspace file already sets
the project-specific subset):

```jsonc
{
  // Terminal profiles (Windows)
  "terminal.external.windowsExec": "C:\\Windows\\System32\\wsl.exe",
  "terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows": "PowerShell 7",
  "terminal.integrated.profiles.windows": {
    "PowerShell 7": { "path": "C:\\Program Files\\PowerShell\\7\\pwsh.exe" },
    "zsh": { "path": "C:\\Windows\\System32\\wsl.exe", "args": ["-e", "zsh"] }
  },

  // Copilot
  "github.copilot.chat.codesearch.enabled": true,
  "github.copilot.nextEditSuggestions.enabled": true,
  "github.copilot.nextEditSuggestions.allowWhitespaceOnlyChanges": false,

  // Spell checker — add your language
  "cSpell.language": "en, da",

  // Notes (if using patricklee.vsnotes)
  "vsnotes.defaultNotePath": "<your-notes-folder>"
}
```

