## Linting and Formatting Configuration

| File | Tool | Purpose |
| --------------------------------- | -------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `.editorconfig` | EditorConfig | Whitespace & encoding conventions |
| `.prettierrc.json` | Prettier | JS/TS/JSON/YAML/MD formatter rules |
| `.prettierignore` | Prettier | Paths Prettier should skip |
| `.markdownlint-cli2.yaml` | markdownlint | Markdown style rules |
| `.hadolint.yaml` | Hadolint | Dockerfile linting rules |
| `backend/pyproject.toml [tool.ruff]` | Ruff | Python linting & formatting |
| `cspell.json` | cSpell | Spell-check dictionary & ignores |
| `eslint.config.js` | ESLint | TypeScript linting (frontend/) |
| `tsconfig.json` | TypeScript | Compiler options (frontend/) |
